/>\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稅局行動宣言：<br />\n<br />\n稅局，納稅人金錢吐納之處。六月以降，香港警隊搬出大量催淚彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈甚或實彈，一一射向香港市民。購置武器，所費不菲，警隊資金何來？稅款必是一大來源。港人金錢，變作供養濫暴警隊的薪水，變作不人道武器還於港人之身，這絕非稅款的正當用途。政府無能，特首執拗難以平息民憤，何解需公帑埋單？<br />\n<br />\n香港市民安分守己，繳納血汗金錢；今民意所指為五大訴求，政府乃人民公僕，理應善用公帑以平眾怒，藉稅款促進訴求之達成以撫民心。然林鄭政府恣意調用港人金錢，屢行政治操作，維護腐敗議會，投稅款入朽壞警隊之血海，廣大市民如何甘心將夙夜辛勞所得，雙手奉上予這毫無公信力的政府？<br />\n<br />\n我等市民將一連三星期到稅局抗議，以示港人之怒，不到五大訴求悉數落實一日不熄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=219861f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=14274937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"cbe53ebf85c12a050a86cf20a872ebe9a93582b7","tid":1788530,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"77ed2e80197bc71b4fbd3d5eaa21b0ef26eb15c2","tid":1788530,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:32:06.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b3e8b4bcec715c23bbdee0d528c2d716859bb39a","tid":1788530,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:39:46.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"98af4328041e9b6f6bbc99768061de4c7bf32b00","tid":1788530,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:46:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7c563559ff823851e27c1568b3bef502f2486e2b","tid":1788530,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"